WEBVTT

00:00:01.412 --> 00:00:04.119
When I first became a doctor

00:00:04.143 --> 00:00:06.148
in Benin City, Nigeria,

00:00:06.172 --> 00:00:09.113
some 30-odd years ago,

00:00:09.137 --> 00:00:13.151
I was drawn to help
people live full lives.

00:00:14.068 --> 00:00:16.967
But often, I found myself
feeling impotent.

00:00:17.524 --> 00:00:21.390
Here I was, a brand-new doctor
with all these skills,

00:00:21.414 --> 00:00:25.645
but I couldn't cure my patients
who had chronic diseases --

00:00:25.669 --> 00:00:30.908
illnesses like heart disease,
asthma, diabetes --